SOFTWARE REQUIREMENT
====================

- Python 2.6 or later (not 3.x)
- wxPython



HOW TO INSTALL
==============

no need to install distribution, just set path.

1. Linux, MacOS

  $ export PATH=$PATH:/somewhere/PDI/bin


2. Windows

  > set PATH=%PATH%;X:\somewhere\PDI\bin

 
